Supported Platforms:

Windows (10 or higher)
MacOS (10.12 Sierra or higher)
Linux (Ubuntu 16.04 or higher)
Browser (Playable on platforms like Itch.io)
Minimum System Requirements:

Processor: Dual-core CPU @ 2.0 GHz
Memory: 4 GB RAM
Graphics: Intel HD Graphics 4000 or equivalent
DirectX: Version 11 (Windows)
Storage: 1 GB available space
Recommended System Requirements:

Processor: Quad-core CPU @ 3.0 GHz
Memory: 8 GB RAM
Graphics: NVIDIA GeForce GTX 960 / AMD Radeon R9 380 or equivalent
DirectX: Version 12 (Windows)
Storage: 2 GB available space
